Setup Instructions
==================

Server-side setup
----------------------------
1. Install Python 2.7 (http://www.python.org/getit/)
2. Install pip (http://www.pip-installer.org/en/latest/installing.html)
3. Run the following command in the same folder that contains `requirements.txt`

    pip install requirements.txt
    
4. Run the appropriate application:

    python websocket_server.py # Websocket Server: on port 8001
    python bottle_server.py    # AJAX Server     : on port 8000

Client-side setup
-----------------
1. Install bower (http://bower.io)
2. From the same folder that contains `bower.json`, run the following command to install any necessary JavaScript packages:

    bower install

Running the examples
--------------------
If the above steps have been followed correctly, it should be possible to view the examples after starting `bottle_server.py` and visiting the following URL:

    http://localhost:8000/index.html
